      "subtitle": {
        "en": "Gateway to Cinque Terre's famous coastal paths."
      },
      "content": {
        "en": "Riomaggiore is typically the first or last village visitors encounter when exploring Cinque Terre by train from La Spezia. This strategic position makes it the natural starting point for the famous Blue Trail and the romantic Via dell'Amore to Manarola. The village's dramatic vertical architecture—houses stacked upon houses climbing the steep valley—creates one of Cinque Terre's most striking skylines."
      }
    },
